      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(horizontal-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> RUBENS SANTORO La casa della fioraria
                                  La maison de la bouque... 
                                  Das raus des blumenmadchehns
                                  the house of the floir or girl  </s>
               <s> XI ESPOSIZIONE D'ARTE DELLA CITTA' DI VENEZIA - MCMXIV</s>
            </p>
            <p rend="writing-mode(vertical-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> Proprietà artistica riservata - 278 </s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="fronte" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <figure>
               <head>La casa della fioraria</head>
               <figDesc> Una donna seduta su dei gradini con in mano dei fiori
               </figDesc>
            </figure>
         </div>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline>
                     <lb/>
                     <s>            Lì 27/9 - 1916. </s>
                  </dateline>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p type="retro">
                     <lb/>            Mia buona Oliva, nemmeno <lb/>            oggi voglio lasciarti senza il mio affettuoso saluto, <lb/>            malgrado la grande attività mi tenga occupato<lb/>            giorno e notte per il cambio di posizioni. <lb/>            Questa notte si forte fu la trincea. Coraggio <lb/>            mia carisfima Oliva. Pensa che il tuo Giovan - <lb/>            nino è con te, per te, t'amo, t'amo tanto <lb/>            tanto affascinatamente, eternamente. Si sempre <lb/>            buona e voglimi bene. Con tutto l'animo<lb/>            mio abbi un soavisfimo bacio dal <lb/>            Oggi mi sono recato a Gorizia. </p>
                  <p type="fronte"/>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <lb/>tuo <signed>
                     <persName>
                        <forename ref="Giovannino">Giovannino</forename>
                     </persName>
                  </signed>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext" part="N">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 125 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
